title: "BroScienceBench: Evaluating Large Language Models on Strength-Training Misinformation"
abstract: >-
  A 246-item benchmark of 42 strength-training myth clusters across 7 categories,
  with held-out, hard, and calibration splits, evaluated under an open-ended
  protocol graded by a validated neutral LLM judge.
